        "`Workspace+Persistence.swift` defaults direct queue discovery to `.ralph/queue.jsonc` before resolved paths exist.",
        "`docs/features/app.md` troubleshooting tells users to confirm `.ralph/queue.jsonc` instead of the configured queue file."
